methods.existingColumn:
The existing column name, from the right table of a join operation.

:return: (io.deephaven.api.ColumnName) the existing column name
methods.newColumn:
The new column name, to be added to the new table.

:return: (io.deephaven.api.ColumnName) the new column name

text:
A join addition represents a new column that should be added as the result
 of a join, brought over from an existing column.
